imports "http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureMap/Element5to4"

group base64Binary(source src : base64BinaryR5, target tgt : base64BinaryR4) extends Element <<type+>> {
  src.value as v -> tgt.value = v "base64BinaryValue";
}

}

}

}
